                     <interp inst="t18190915-237-person2026" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a labourer. On Wednesday the prosecutor came to the workhouse, and gave information, the prisoner did not come there afterward. I have the hat he left in the room of his own.</p>
